{"type":null,"faqId":49435,"title":"发送信息","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"发信息\"XE \"发短信\"XE \"发送短信\"XE \"发送彩信\"XE \"添加彩信主题\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189109\" style=\"width:0.18680556in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“信息”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在信息列表界面，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189110\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击收件人文本框，输入联系人姓名或手机号码。也可点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189111\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”进入联系人列表界面，直接选择联系人或群组。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>点击信息文本框，输入信息内容。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189112\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189113\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，选择附件类型，然后选择要附加的项目。如果您添加的是照片、图片等文件，此时短信会自动转换为彩信。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 5  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189114\" style=\"width:0.20625in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”或“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189115\" style=\"width:0.20625in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5179","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294354000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":9,"times":3,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}